rows.label: qst701304_msg0002
rows.name:
Why... If you die,
it's all for nothing.

rows.label: qst701304_msg0003
rows.name: But it seems he achieved his goal.

rows.label: qst701304_msg0004
rows.name:
Let's at least deliver
this to Sarah-san.

rows.label: qst701304_msg0005
rows.name:
...Because it's what he was willing
to risk his life to prove.

rows.label: qst701304_msg0007
rows.name:
But before that, we have to make a
grave for the traveling performer.
I want to let him rest in peace.
